    <div xml:id="PN254-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. <gap quantity="5" reason="lost" unit="character"/>kayamaṉār pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
     </div>
    <div xml:id="PN254">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>iḷaiyaru mutiyarum vēṟupulam paṭara</l>
<l>veṭuppa veḻāay mārpamaṇ pulla</l>
<l>viṭaiccurat tiṟutta maḷḷa viḷartta</l>
<l>vaḷaiyil vaṟuṅkai yōccik kiḷaiyu</l>
<l>ḷiṉṉa ṉāyiṉa ṉiḷaiyō ṉeṉṟu</l>
<l>niṉṉurai cellu māyiṉ maṟṟu</l>
<l>muṉṉūrp paḻuṉiya kōḷi yālattup</l>
<l>puḷḷār yāṇart taṟṟē yeṉmakaṉ</l>
<l>vaḷaṉuñ cemmalu memakkeṉa nāḷu</l>
<l>māṉātu pukaḻu maṉṉai</l>
<l>yāṅkā kuvaḷko laḷiyaḷ ṭāṉē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="2ab">You who won’t rise when roused, </l>
<l corresp="1">while young and old set out for another region, </l>
<l corresp="2cd">  while [your] chest embraces the earth, </l>
<l corresp="3a-c">o warrior who tarries in the middle of the desert, </l>
<l corresp="5">saying “the young man became like this” </l>
<l corresp="3d-4">among [his] kin, wielding empty hand without bangles that became bare, </l>
<l corresp="6">if you [thus] say your word </l>
<l>the front village will be thus: of a fertility on which </l>
<l corresp="7-8c">birds become full, in the banyan tree. </l>
<l corresp="10">The mother who praises [him] unendingly, </l>
<l corresp="8d-9">saying “my son is for us prosperity and excellence”, </l>
<l corresp="11">what will become of her? Pitiable she is. </l>
</lg>
    </div>
